# Docs/manual/manual-entries-archive/

Per-module CODE_MANUAL entries that were prepared as paste-ready snippets
during autonomous research rounds, retained here as historical archive
after the content was merged into the canonical `Docs/manual/CODE_MANUAL.md`.

These files do not carry independent canonical authority. The canonical
operator-level code reference is `Docs/manual/CODE_MANUAL.md`.

This directory is created per the 2026-04-24 Math82 repo cleanup
(Phase A relocation of root-level CODE_MANUAL-*-Entry.txt files).
